The paper discusses the security and privacy challenges of deploying neural networks on edge devices, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also covers the landscape of attacks and defenses on neural networks, which involves machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact on system security, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
